<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="19a" n="4">날마다 나식 니</sent>
<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="19a" n="5">봄에 됴흔 鴉靑 웃오 흰 깁 속오시오</sent>

<sent type="main" lang="kor" page="19b" n="1">녀에 장  모시뵈 赤杉이오</sent>
